Date: Sun, 28 Mar 2021 21:00:18 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] rockchip: add support for OrangePi R1 Plus

Hardware Specification:
  CPU: RockChip RK3328 (4 cores)
  RAM: 1GB DDR4
  Ethernet: 2x 1000 Base-T
  Flash: SPI-NOR 16 MB (mx25l12835f)
  LED: SYS, LAN, WAN
  MicroSD Slot x 1
  Button: Reset
  USB:1x 2.0
  Serial1: 13 Pin pin-header
  Serial2: 3 Pin debug port
  Type-C: for power input
  Power Supply: DC 5V/2A

Installation:
  Write the image to SD Card with dd.

Signed-off-by: AmadeusGhost <amadeus@jmu.edu.cn>
Signed-off-by: Tianling Shen <cnsztl@immortalwrt.org>
